data.description: Don't miss this 2-story property that is now on the market! It boasts an inviting interior with wood-look floors and a neutral palette. The spacious great room is perfect for family gatherings. A modern kitchen shines with recessed lighting, a mosaic tile backsplash, SS appliances, a pantry, granite counters, and a center island with a breakfast bar. The large main bedroom includes a sitting area and features a private bathroom with dual sinks, a soothing tub, and a walk-in closet. A versatile den can serve as an additional bedroom or an office. A spacious loft offers a great space for an entertainment center or game room. Outside, the relaxing backyard is equipped with a covered patio, seating areas, and a refreshing pool. This home is a must-see for those seeking comfort and style!
